Appointment-Confirmations Page:

Used Tools are: 
1. Python - as scripting language during the process
2. SQL Lite - for storing data in the database
3. JQuery - Inorder to send query strings to retrieve data
4. HTML - For developing the Front-end of the web-application
5. Bootstrap - For proper format of the web page. 
6. VMware (Ubuntu-Linux) - environment to develop and debug the web-page.
7. Flask - was used as a framework 
8. REST - Web service was used


OUTPUT: Finished the Project successfully in 2 days. I have used 3rd day for improvising and documentation. 


Versions:

Python 2.7.3
Sql Lite 3
Javascript - JQuery






